{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty."}]}],"name":"url"},{"name":"headers","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is useful for:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Regional compliance","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network monitoring"}]},{"text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Firewall restrictions"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"while preserving all headers and request body content."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}]},{"code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}}}